data.description: Great opportunity!!! 5+ Acres with a 3 Bd/2 Ba, 4-sided Brick, Ranch house. The house offers a large open Living Room, separate Dining Room and Laundry Room, Large bedrooms, Full Covered Patio overlooking the rear of the property. Large partially finished basement with a single car/boat garage. The possibilities for this property are endless. Conveniently located near schools and shopping. Has a rural feel, yet close to everything! SOLD AS-IS.  INCLUDES Parcel ID: 0547 011 and Parcel ID: 0547 018
